	These home-loving, gentle demihumans are also known as halflings.
They are the nimblest of races which, combined with their small stature, makes
them excel at dexterity-related activities, whether it be thievery or
exploring tangled brush.  Their strength and piety are slightly less than
those of humans.

Initial stat modifiers:

STR: -1
DEX: +2
PTY: -1
